--- TIMER REGISTERS ---

Disable Timer before changing the prescaler:
TIMGn_Tx_EN

Prescaler Register
TIMGn_Tx_DIVIDER

Timer counter direction Register
TIMGn_Tx_INCREASE

Set new counter value should be incremented each interupt handling
TIMGn_Tx_LOAD_HI

Before reading the value from the timer this register should be set
TIMGn_TxUPDATE_REG

Timer counter value registers (32bit each)
TIMGn_TxHI_REG
TIMGn_TxLO_REG

TIMGn_Tx_EN = 1
TIMGn_Tx_INCREASE = 1
TIMGn_Tx_AUTORELOAD = 0
TIMGn_Tx_DIVIDER = 1024
TIMGn_Tx_EDGE_INT_EN = 0
TIMGn_Tx_LEVEL_INT_EN = 0
TIMGn_Tx_ALARM_EN  = 0

110 0000010000000000 000  0000000000
